<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="turn-a-deaf-ear-to">turn a deaf ear (to)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(对…) 置之不理：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Many of them turned a deaf ear to his advice, even though they knew it to be valuable. 
他们中的许多人对他的建议置之不理，即使他们知道他的建议是有益的。</p></div></div>